Join the Invasion with up to four players in this fast-paced, objective-based shoot 'em up! Beam down to hand-drawn neighborhoods to steal enemy intel, sabotage the Agency's plans, and mutate into an array of alien forms for ultimate chaos. Carve out your own gameplay path to the enemy HQ and take down the boss at the end of each mission map; reap the rewards through unlockable mutations, weapons, abilities, and more!

Experience this all-new re-imagining of the original Alien Hominid on PlayStation® today from The Behemoth, creators of co-op adventures like Castle Crashers and BattleBlock Theater!

Every question must have its answer! Embark on the luxury cruise of Agatha Christie - Death on the Nile, departing for PlayStation 5 on September 2025.

Death on the Nile is an adventure-detective game, offering a fresh twist on Agatha Christie’s famous story. Set in the lively 1970s, play as Hercule Poirot and detective Jane Royce as they solve two connected mysteries. Dive into a journey filled with intrigue, deception, and unexpected revelations.
